@startuml navigation-shell-state
' Context: navigation
' SDD: PROM-MULTI-ACCOUNT, PROM-SHAREABLE-LINK
' Revision: 2026-07-18

title Navigation — shell state machine (per account in focus)

state InboxVisible
state ChatOpen
state GroupShell

[*] --> InboxVisible

InboxVisible --> ChatOpen : OpenPeerOnFocusedAccount\n/ ConversationOpened
InboxVisible --> ChatOpen : OpenConversationOnAccount\n/ ConversationOpened
InboxVisible --> GroupShell : [account gruppo in focus]

ChatOpen --> InboxVisible : CloseConversation
GroupShell --> GroupShell : OpenGroupChat

note right of ChatOpen
  OpenFromPushTap e OpenFromShareableLink
  usano OpenConversationOnAccount
end note

@enduml
